*   ## **_JON MOXLEY DEF. KEVIN KNIGHT_**_(13:44)_
    

Moxley wins with a brutal new chokehold. Post match the Death Riders go to beat down JETSpeed until Darby comes out to even the odds. He also gets beaten down until WILL OSPREAY RETURNS!!!!

Ospreay will take the fight to the Death Riders at Forbidden Door. Get your friends, Ospreay and Darby will get theirs.

## **_LIGHTS OUT STEEL CAGE MATCH AT FORBIDDEN DOOR!!!_**

