*   ## **_EDGE AND CHRISTIAN HAVE FINALLY REUNITED!!!!!!!!!!_**
    

Christian runs out to save Edge from an FTR beat down. He's almost attacked by Nick Wayne and Kip Sabian but Edge saves Christian.

They come face to face, Christian hands SPIKE over to Edge and they EMBRACED!!!! ❤️

